snippet.title: Last Sentinel - Official Reveal Trailer | Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
Set decades from now in a reconstructed Tokyo, you play as Hiromi Shoda in Last Sentinel, a narrative-focused, open-world action game from Lightspeed Studios.
